OL,3,CPeter Kay 'locals only' homecoming
OL,4,Ccharity shows sells out in a hour
OL,6,FPeter Kay's first shows in his
OL,7,Fhometown for 23 years sold out within
OL,8,Fa hour after tickets went on sale for
OL,9,Flocals only.
OL,11,FThe comedian will be performing four
OL,12,Fshows in July 2026 at The Albert Halls
OL,13,Fin Bolton for the first time since
OL,14,F2003.
OL,16,FAll profits from the surprise shows
OL,17,Fwill be donated to Bolton Hospice,
OL,18,Fwhich Peter Kay described as an
OL,19,F"amazing charity".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
