OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1777126303
OL,3,CPeter Kay 'locals only' homecoming
OL,4,Ccharity shows sells out in a hour
OL,6,FTickets for the gigs, between the 9-11
OL,7,FJuly 2026, opened at 10am on 24 April
OL,8,Fand were snapped up almost instantly,
OL,9,Fleaving many hopefuls disappointed as
OL,10,Fdemand far outstripped supply.
OL,12,FOnly a select few were able to buy
OL,13,Ftickets - with sales limited to those
OL,14,Fwho live in a BL postcode.
OL,16,FAnnouncing the shows, Peter said: "I
OL,17,Fcan't believe it's 23 years since my
OL,18,FAlbert Halls shows, so I reckon it's
OL,19,Fabout time I came back. I'm really
OL,20,Flooking forward to it.
OL,26,@xD@cOU
